  %a{:href=>"http://d3js.org"}="d3."
  Mike works for the NYTimes and is responsible for the awesome enrichment that the
  %a{:href=>"http://www.nytimes.com/interactive/2014/01/11/us/politics/who-controls-the-states-and-where-they-stand.html"}="articles"
  receive.  
  %br
  %br

%h3="Automation"
%p
  Who doesn't love automation.  I am a firm beliver in never doing anything twice.  The "Internet of Things" has me really exicted as well.  Sites like
  %a{:href=>"http://www.ifttt.com"}
    "If This Then That"
  have so much potential to automate things in a normalize and elegant way.

